==Korean==
===Noun===
'''버드나무''' ('''''beodeu'''-namu'')
#(''literally, "willow tree" cf. German [[Weidenbaum]]'') [[willow]], '''[[withy]]''' cf. German '''[[Weide]]'''

====Alternative spellings====
*버들나모 (''beodeul-namo'') (''obsolete'')

====Synonyms====
*[[버들]] (''beodeul, -deur'') 
*유 ([[柳]], ''yu'') 
*양 ([[楊]], ''yang'')

====Related terms====
*[[부드럽다]] (''budeureobda, -reopda'') To be [[soft]], [[tender]], [[mellow]], [[mild]]
*[[부들부들]]하다 (''budeul-budeul-hada'') To be [[soft]], [[tender]], [[mellow]], [[mild]]
*[[부들부들]] (''budeul-budeul, -deur'') (''adverb'') [[trembling]]
*[[시들다]] (''sideulda'') To '''[[wither]]''' (''probably cognate with '''[[withe]]''''')

